    <item>
      <title>新华社：中国监管机构寻求改善房地产市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/china-s-regulators-seek-improvements-to-property-market-xinhua</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据新华社周日报道，中国监管机构将试图通过改善土地使用、税收和其他金融措施来提振房地产市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/china-s-regulators-seek-improvements-to-property-market-xinhua</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 12:53:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员准备迎接韩国政治僵局带来的更多波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/traders-brace-for-more-volatility-on-korea-s-political-stalemate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着周一市场重新开市，交易员们正准备迎接韩国资产持续波动的局面，由于周末的戏剧性事件加深了韩国的政治危机，韩元和股市最初面临压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/traders-brace-for-more-volatility-on-korea-s-political-stalemate</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 12:53:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党计划“改革”规划系统以实现住房目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/uk-government-will-overhaul-planning-system-to-hit-house-targets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副首相安吉拉·雷纳在《每日电讯报》上撰文称，工党计划“彻底改革”规划系统，以实现其五年内在英国建造 150 万套新房的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/uk-government-will-overhaul-planning-system-to-hit-house-targets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 12:51:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普幽灵引发最后一轮利率调整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/specter-of-trump-spurs-a-final-round-of-interest-rate-moves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫引发全球贸易动荡的可能性上升之前，四大洲的央行将在未来一周对借贷成本做出最后一系列调整。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/specter-of-trump-spurs-a-final-round-of-interest-rate-moves</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克抗议活动引发的停电影响到赞比亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/mozambique-power-output-cut-by-protests-targeting-infrastructure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于针对 10 月 9 日有争议的选举的持续抗议活动导致两座主要发电厂的产量中断，包括首都马普托在内的莫桑比克南部地区的电力供应减少了约三分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/mozambique-power-output-cut-by-protests-targeting-infrastructure</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 16:39:43 GMT</pubDate>
